<AUTHOR>Smoothbassman</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>The new Ram is an exciting new vehicle in the Dodge lineup. The design is aggressive the interior is beautiful the motor is solid and it's incredibly quiet on the highway. The rear 4 link suspension makes this truck ride so smooth it feels like a luxury vehicle. The wrap around console keeps everything within reach and everything is where you expect it to be. The nighttime display is very nice. Hands down I drove an F-150 and a Silverado and this was the smoothest and best looking truck of them all. Also the price was the cheapest of all of them! You can't go wrong with the new 2009 Ram</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>I sprung for the navigation and remote start package. It's really nice! Dodge has done a good job with that. The media center is so cool with the DVD in the dash. All the storage areas in the truck make everything seem very organized </FAVORITE>
